node.text: For this entry of #tgrtested, we took the liberty of trying out @trekbikes' new Slash 9.9. Our thoughts? Well, it might be as aggressive as single-crown bikes get, but it's also a versatile tool that will make a good rider feel like a great rider in just about any kind of terrain. Trek describes the rig as “monster truck meets magic carpet,” and that was all it took for us to see what was up. Full #tgrtested review at the link in bio! // 📸 @rax_mitter

node.text:
This Summer, we invited multisport athlete & TGR Optics team member @kcdeane to Jackson for a week of playing (and ripping) in the Tetons. Each day, a different Jackson local took KC out for an adventure. 

First up, @rowdyflow took KC to @jacksonhole to put the new upper mountain trails to the test. When it came time for KC to get his flow on in TGR’s new Accomplice shades, he was definitely ready to throw down on some brown pow. Lucky for him, young buck Rowdy showed him a few  of his favorite hits (don’t worry, he saved a couple stashes). 

It might not be a competition, but c’mon, who’s winning?
